def my_check_function (dataset):
    '''     '''
    print('  ( , ):')

    print(dataset.isna().mean())
    print()
    print('   ,  :')
    print(dataset.duplicated().sum())
    print('  :')
    print(dataset.duplicated().mean())
    print()
    print('  :')
    display(dataset.describe())

           df['sqlex_last_solved_task_number'] - df['sqlex_last_solved_task_number'].shift(1)))

(df.insert(8, 'course_day_cnt', 
           df['course_current'] - df['course_current'].shift(1)))

           df['stepic_python_current'] - df['stepic_python_current'].shift(1)))
